                    "id": "64e949ba-7f7e-4e0f-b1a9-f097831cc6e4",
                    "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Today, we're going to make Healing Pills. These pills are more effective than mushrooms or regular bandages. They are not as effective as Healing Potions, but they are easier to use in the middle of combat.",
                    "emotion": "1",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "d6ea7c9e-3a7e-4cc9-a88a-c637c3c83429",
                    "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "It takes ten Puffball mushrooms, a clove of garlic, the petals of a calendula flower, and gelatin from seaweed to make a batch of three pills.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "72301788-5444-4d34-b851-0a8eff2a3402",
                    "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "You will get to take away a bottle with three Healing Pills. However, if you have ten Puffballs with you, you can take six pills with you. The other plant ingredients can be found in the garden.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "e6c886a1-0dfe-4c6d-8003-ef1ee32b05b6",
                    "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Let's get started. I've placed all the ingredients you will need at your stations.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
